  "body": "When sending a query to `eth_estimate` gas, it returns `0` for a normal transaction:\n\n```\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_estimateGas\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0x343c98e2b6e49bc0fed722c2a269f3814ddd1533\",\"to\":\"0x990ccf8a0de58091c028d6ff76bb235ee67c1c39\", \"value\":\"0x3e8\"}],\"id\":13080}\n```\n\nResponse\n\n```\n{\n    \"id\": 13080,\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n    \"result\": \"0x0\"\n}\n```\n",
